MBOMBELA – The city and surrounding areas were heavily affected by power outages on Thursday morning. Well-known resident Thea Rix advised that it was most certainly not load-shedding. A warning of possible load-shedding for last night had been issued, but was not implemented. Rix said the outages on Thursday were widespread, but were not load-shedding. She urged people to report power outages so that the faults could be attended to. Report any issues to 0861-626-62352 and keep an eye on the Mbombela Electricity & Water Information group on Facebook for more information.   